{
  "video_id": "USnf5kbsMlg",
  "title": "The role of human emotions in science and research | Ilona Stengel",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12752.0,
      "end_time": 14928.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a scientist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14952.0,
      "end_time": 18400.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m a big fan of Star Trek,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18640.0,
      "end_time": 20540.0,
      "text": "especially of Mr. Spock."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21781.0,
      "end_time": 23807.0,
      "text": "Mr. Spock is a scientist as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23831.0,
      "end_time": 25988.0,
      "text": "and at the same time, he&#39;s the first [officer]"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26120.0,
      "end_time": 28980.0,
      "text": "of the starship Enterprise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29400.0,
      "end_time": 32124.0,
      "text": "and during the adventures of the Enterprise crew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32148.000000000004,
      "end_time": 34274.0,
      "text": "he and his colleagues are dealing a lot"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34298.0,
      "end_time": 38940.0,
      "text": "with the presence or absence of Mr. Spock&#39;s emotions."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39924.0,
      "end_time": 43631.0,
      "text": "Mr. Spock is half-human and half-Vulcan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43655.0,
      "end_time": 46313.0,
      "text": "and Vulcans are an alien race"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46337.0,
      "end_time": 49520.0,
      "text": "who learn to control and suppress their feelings"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49760.0,
      "end_time": 51900.0,
      "text": "and to act purely out of logic."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51995.0,
      "end_time": 54709.0,
      "text": "As Mr. Spock is only half-Vulcan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54734.0,
      "end_time": 60291.0,
      "text": "he sees himself constantly in conflict in between logic and emotions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 60315.0,
      "end_time": 62339.0,
      "text": "and as he&#39;s part of a team,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 62363.0,
      "end_time": 65242.0,
      "text": "the whole crew is struggling with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65266.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67380.0,
      "text": "is analyzing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67620.0,
      "end_time": 68887.0,
      "text": "and is making fun of this conflict."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69566.0,
      "end_time": 72473.0,
      "text": "And also the fans of Star Trek watch with amusement"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72497.0,
      "end_time": 74728.0,
      "text": "this seemingly contradictory behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75155.0,
      "end_time": 78268.0,
      "text": "They find it quite fascinating."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79362.0,
      "end_time": 81270.0,
      "text": "And the matter is a golden thread"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81520.0,
      "end_time": 84715.0,
      "text": "through the whole Star Trek series and movies from the &#39;60s until today."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85910.0,
      "end_time": 87916.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s actually what I want to talk about today:"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87940.0,
      "end_time": 90265.0,
      "text": "the role of emotions in science."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 91353.0,
      "end_time": 95696.0,
      "text": "We tend to think that science is all about facts and logic"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95720.0,
      "end_time": 100290.0,
      "text": "and human feelings are often neglected or considered an obstacle to get rid of."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100989.0,
      "end_time": 105300.0,
      "text": "I would like to suggest that emotions are as important in science"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 105324.0,
      "end_time": 107585.0,
      "text": "as they are in any other part of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 108195.0,
      "end_time": 110377.0,
      "text": "Science is made by humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 110402.0,
      "end_time": 112107.0,
      "text": "and as human beings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 112131.0,
      "end_time": 115945.0,
      "text": "even if we try hard, we cannot get rid of our emotions."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 116704.0,
      "end_time": 118883.0,
      "text": "So instead of fighting them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 118907.0,
      "end_time": 122455.0,
      "text": "I believe that even in science, we should make use of our feelings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 122479.0,
      "end_time": 124685.0,
      "text": "because for breakthroughs and innovation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 124709.0,
      "end_time": 127320.0,
      "text": "they are equally important as facts and logic."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 129256.0,
      "end_time": 131216.0,
      "text": "I will come back to Mr. Spock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 131240.0,
      "end_time": 136392.0,
      "text": "but first let me share my experience on the role of emotions in science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 136416.0,
      "end_time": 139305.0,
      "text": "and one story in particular kept me thinking about it"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 139329.0,
      "end_time": 141260.0,
      "text": "for the last couple of years."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 141940.0,
      "end_time": 146195.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m working in research on organic light-emitting diodes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 146219.0,
      "end_time": 147742.0,
      "text": "so-called OLEDs."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 148233.0,
      "end_time": 150238.0,
      "text": "This is how you might know them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150262.0,
      "end_time": 152516.0,
      "text": "as new generation of displays."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 153262.0,
      "end_time": 157587.0,
      "text": "OLEDs are more and more used in smartphone displays and TV screens."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 157611.0,
      "end_time": 162317.0,
      "text": "They make them appear bright, truly colorful and bendable."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 163963.0,
      "end_time": 165214.0,
      "text": "This is how they look like"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 165238.0,
      "end_time": 167846.0,
      "text": "in the research lab of my physicist colleagues."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 168979.0,
      "end_time": 171170.0,
      "text": "And this is what I, as a chemist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 171194.0,
      "end_time": 173637.0,
      "text": "have in mind when I think about them."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 173662.0,
      "end_time": 176527.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve loved it ever since I started to work on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 177415.0,
      "end_time": 179611.0,
      "text": "So I didn&#39;t really like the news"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 179635.0,
      "end_time": 181953.0,
      "text": "when the company I had been working for --"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 181977.0,
      "end_time": 184179.0,
      "text": "that was my previous employer --"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 184203.0,
      "end_time": 187400.0,
      "text": "announced that they wanted to stop OLED research."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 188159.0,
      "end_time": 191900.0,
      "text": "At the time, the management had reasons for this decision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 191114.0,
      "end_time": 193532.0,
      "text": "and the company handled it very well, actually."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 193556.0,
      "end_time": 195336.0,
      "text": "Nobody lost their jobs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 195360.0,
      "end_time": 198106.0,
      "text": "and everybody was rewarded for their performed work."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 199430.0,
      "end_time": 200457.0,
      "text": "What I want to show you today"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 200481.0,
      "end_time": 203403.0,
      "text": "is what happened with my scientist colleagues and me"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 203427.0,
      "end_time": 206164.0,
      "text": "during the time in between the announcement"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 206188.0,
      "end_time": 208465.0,
      "text": "and the last working day on our project."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 209670.0,
      "end_time": 212916.0,
      "text": "Consider it a small case study on emotions in science."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 214454.0,
      "end_time": 219231.0,
      "text": "In 2015, our research team had grown to more than 80 people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 219255.0,
      "end_time": 222724.0,
      "text": "and even after the announcement that our project was discontinued,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 222748.0,
      "end_time": 225236.0,
      "text": "we could not stop working from one day to another."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 225759.0,
      "end_time": 229690.0,
      "text": "It took several months to bring all activities to a sound end"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 229714.0,
      "end_time": 232602.0,
      "text": "and to find new jobs within the company for everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 233880.0,
      "end_time": 234421.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s what happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 234445.0,
      "end_time": 237910.0,
      "text": "Even though we knew that we were working on a project"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 237116.0,
      "end_time": 239112.0,
      "text": "that was to be stopped,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 239136.0,
      "end_time": 242218.0,
      "text": "during those months our output hit the roof."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 243377.0,
      "end_time": 246757.0,
      "text": "We were actually working on two different OLED projects:"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 246781.0,
      "end_time": 250774.0,
      "text": "first, the development of materials for blue-shining OLEDs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 250798.0,
      "end_time": 253434.0,
      "text": "which had started in 2001;"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 253458.0,
      "end_time": 259130.0,
      "text": "and second, materials for green OLEDs, which had started in 2014."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 259154.0,
      "end_time": 262472.0,
      "text": "And the results I show you here concern the green OLED project."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 263297.0,
      "end_time": 266290.0,
      "text": "In the graph, you can see how the lifetime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 266530.0,
      "end_time": 269840.0,
      "text": "which is a crucial measure for the durability of our devices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 269864.0,
      "end_time": 271520.0,
      "text": "developed over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 272677.0,
      "end_time": 276748.0,
      "text": "In 2015, just half a year into the project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 276772.0,
      "end_time": 279178.0,
      "text": "we were told to scale down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 279202.0,
      "end_time": 282377.0,
      "text": "to stop working on the project as soon as possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 282401.0,
      "end_time": 284194.0,
      "text": "and to start over in other jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 284987.0,
      "end_time": 287528.0,
      "text": "Nevertheless, from this time on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 287552.0,
      "end_time": 290555.0,
      "text": "our results continued to improve rapidly."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 292970.0,
      "end_time": 293246.0,
      "text": "How did that happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 295700.0,
      "end_time": 299332.0,
      "text": "After the announcement, pretty quickly, colleagues started leaving the team,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 299357.0,
      "end_time": 301793.0,
      "text": "and soon, we were left in a small group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 301817.0,
      "end_time": 304861.0,
      "text": "all pretty much sharing the same attitude of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 304885.0,
      "end_time": 307448.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m going to be the last person leaving the ship.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 308410.0,
      "end_time": 309882.0,
      "text": "What I mean is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 309906.0,
      "end_time": 313935.0,
      "text": "while the number of scientists working on the project was decreasing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 313959.0,
      "end_time": 317642.0,
      "text": "the dedication of people remaining grew dramatically."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 319540.0,
      "end_time": 322633.0,
      "text": "And also, a new and more intense team spirit formed."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 323543.0,
      "end_time": 326770.0,
      "text": "We all shared the same passion for our work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 326794.0,
      "end_time": 330700.0,
      "text": "we all were sad that it was about to end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 330950.0,
      "end_time": 333865.0,
      "text": "and we all wanted to show that we could turn our ideas into reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 334647.0,
      "end_time": 337488.0,
      "text": "We felt that we belonged to something bigger."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 338790.0,
      "end_time": 340369.0,
      "text": "And furthermore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 340393.0,
      "end_time": 344850.0,
      "text": "our project was less and less in the focus of the management,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 344109.0,
      "end_time": 346816.0,
      "text": "because they started to think about new projects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 346840.0,
      "end_time": 348537.0,
      "text": "restructuring and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 349434.0,
      "end_time": 352157.0,
      "text": "This resulted in additional freedom"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 352181.0,
      "end_time": 356203.0,
      "text": "and the possibility to take a few things into our own hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 357100.0,
      "end_time": 361746.0,
      "text": "Of course, more freedom also means more responsibility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 361771.0,
      "end_time": 365637.0,
      "text": "which we were happy to take, because we believed in our work."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 365989.0,
      "end_time": 367661.0,
      "text": "We felt empowered."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 368589.0,
      "end_time": 370385.0,
      "text": "And these three pillars --"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 370409.0,
      "end_time": 375236.0,
      "text": "dedication, belonging and empowerment --"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 375261.0,
      "end_time": 378706.0,
      "text": "worked together in a kind of self-reinforcing cycle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 378730.0,
      "end_time": 380879.0,
      "text": "and the closer we got to shutdown,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 380903.0,
      "end_time": 382562.0,
      "text": "the better our output became."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 383241.0,
      "end_time": 385796.0,
      "text": "So we were working with such personal engagement"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 385821.0,
      "end_time": 388107.0,
      "text": "on a project already sentenced to death"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 388131.0,
      "end_time": 391530.0,
      "text": "because we felt connected to something meaningful."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 393440.0,
      "end_time": 398401.0,
      "text": "Of course, it was also a hard and sometimes frustrating time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 398425.0,
      "end_time": 400441.0,
      "text": "but we were sitting together in the lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 400465.0,
      "end_time": 402544.0,
      "text": "or occasionally in the café,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 402569.0,
      "end_time": 405926.0,
      "text": "sharing our sadness about the end of our project"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 405950.0,
      "end_time": 408481.0,
      "text": "as well as the joy in our work."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 408505.0,
      "end_time": 413954.0,
      "text": "So overall, we had a very intense and mesmerizingly exciting time."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 414466.0,
      "end_time": 418370.0,
      "text": "And the lifetime we finally obtained for our materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 418394.0,
      "end_time": 421933.0,
      "text": "was on one level with already commercialized materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 421957.0,
      "end_time": 424740.0,
      "text": "for green OLEDs at the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 424980.0,
      "end_time": 426637.0,
      "text": "and we achieved this within just one year."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 427431.0,
      "end_time": 430479.0,
      "text": "And those results helped our employer"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 430503.0,
      "end_time": 432796.0,
      "text": "to sell the patents for real value."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 434923.0,
      "end_time": 438109.0,
      "text": "Now, let me tell you the same story"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 438133.0,
      "end_time": 441856.0,
      "text": "with different characters and a slightly different operation."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 442341.0,
      "end_time": 444510.0,
      "text": "The story is part of Star Trek."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 444602.0,
      "end_time": 447215.0,
      "text": "And sorry for those of you who haven&#39;t seen the movies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 447239.0,
      "end_time": 449205.0,
      "text": "but I need to introduce a spoiler here."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 450643.0,
      "end_time": 455330.0,
      "text": "After Mr. Spock sacrificed himself to save the starship Enterprise"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 455355.0,
      "end_time": 457655.0,
      "text": "at the end of Star Trek II,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 457679.0,
      "end_time": 459246.0,
      "text": "Captain Kirk and his core team"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 459270.0,
      "end_time": 463472.0,
      "text": "were determined to hunt through the universe to search for Spock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 463497.0,
      "end_time": 466810.0,
      "text": "even though they could see only very little chance"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 466105.0,
      "end_time": 467504.0,
      "text": "in finding him alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 468393.0,
      "end_time": 471193.0,
      "text": "And Starfleet Command did not give them permission"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 471218.0,
      "end_time": 473327.0,
      "text": "nor a starship to do so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 473351.0,
      "end_time": 476772.0,
      "text": "so they took it very passionately into their own hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 476796.0,
      "end_time": 478683.0,
      "text": "to travel out to find Spock."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 479657.0,
      "end_time": 483575.0,
      "text": "And after dealing with great challenges, they eventually found Spock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 483599.0,
      "end_time": 486933.0,
      "text": "and he happily and gratefully joined the team again."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 488235.0,
      "end_time": 491783.0,
      "text": "He could feel the dedication and the connection of his team"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 491807.0,
      "end_time": 495251.0,
      "text": "towards their project, which was to save him"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 495275.0,
      "end_time": 496806.0,
      "text": "and to hold the crew together."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 498172.0,
      "end_time": 502880.0,
      "text": "And over the years, over the episodes of the saga,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 502112.0,
      "end_time": 503700.0,
      "text": "Mr. Spock came to realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 503724.0,
      "end_time": 508743.0,
      "text": "that the combination of both logic and emotions"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 508767.0,
      "end_time": 513568.0,
      "text": "is crucial for facing challenges and exploring new worlds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 513592.0,
      "end_time": 515646.0,
      "text": "and there was no contradiction anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 517150.0,
      "end_time": 522213.0,
      "text": "So the storyline here for both our OLED story and Star Trek"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 522238.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525437.0,
      "text": "is actually the basic setting for a lot of breakthrough stories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 525461.0,
      "end_time": 527182.0,
      "text": "in and out of science."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 528279.0,
      "end_time": 531882.0,
      "text": "The main characters are all part of a great team."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 532915.0,
      "end_time": 537352.0,
      "text": "All team members show a huge dedication towards reaching their goal."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 538710.0,
      "end_time": 542147.0,
      "text": "They strive to seize all the freedom they can get,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 542171.0,
      "end_time": 545336.0,
      "text": "and they take the responsibility they need to take."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 547299.0,
      "end_time": 550617.0,
      "text": "During the time our OLED project was nearing the end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 550641.0,
      "end_time": 554290.0,
      "text": "I received one piece of advice several times."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 555218.0,
      "end_time": 556868.0,
      "text": "\"Don&#39;t take it to your heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 557591.0,
      "end_time": 559361.0,
      "text": "You can work on something else.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 560456.0,
      "end_time": 561949.0,
      "text": "If I had followed it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 561973.0,
      "end_time": 565663.0,
      "text": "it would have saved me several depressed evenings"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 565687.0,
      "end_time": 566852.0,
      "text": "and many tears,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 568950.0,
      "end_time": 569508.0,
      "text": "but at the same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 569532.0,
      "end_time": 575800.0,
      "text": "I would have failed to gain a great deal in personal development and happiness."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 576375.0,
      "end_time": 579710.0,
      "text": "And as the same is true for my colleagues and our whole project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 579734.0,
      "end_time": 581463.0,
      "text": "we would have achieved far less."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 582614.0,
      "end_time": 586772.0,
      "text": "So of course, science should be based on facts and logic."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 587720.0,
      "end_time": 591172.0,
      "text": "When I say we should use our emotions in science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 591196.0,
      "end_time": 594554.0,
      "text": "I do not suggest we should use feelings instead of facts."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 595321.0,
      "end_time": 598659.0,
      "text": "But I say we should not be afraid of using our feelings"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 598683.0,
      "end_time": 602447.0,
      "text": "to implement and to catalyze fact-based science and innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 603229.0,
      "end_time": 606482.0,
      "text": "Emotions and logic do not oppose each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 606967.0,
      "end_time": 609760.0,
      "text": "They complement each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 609100.0,
      "end_time": 610949.0,
      "text": "and they reinforce each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 612317.0,
      "end_time": 616577.0,
      "text": "The feeling of being dedicated to something meaningful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 616601.0,
      "end_time": 619766.0,
      "text": "of belonging to something bigger"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 619790.0,
      "end_time": 621760.0,
      "text": "and of being empowered"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 621784.0,
      "end_time": 624545.0,
      "text": "is crucial for creativity and innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 626630.0,
      "end_time": 627563.0,
      "text": "Whatever you are working on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 628643.0,
      "end_time": 630111.0,
      "text": "make sure that it matters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 631254.0,
      "end_time": 633515.0,
      "text": "and take it to your heart as much as you like."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 634642.0,
      "end_time": 635793.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 635817.0,
      "end_time": 640563.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}